text: Hi <@U07VAD9SL1G> - we won't have that same widget launcher when in the WebView for the mobile SDK. <@U07JHRHGYBV> - can you advise on any other mechanisms available to a mobile app to close the WebView?
Hi <@U07VAD9SL1G> <@U07ARLLF39N> , only way to close the WebView is through a back press. There are no other mechanisms available.
